      <p class="lead text-center">Strava Segment Hunter will generate leaderboards for your club based on the Strava Club ID. There is a video below showing the steps to obtain this ID. <br><a class="text-white"
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qTjWocDQLg&feature=youtu.be"><u>Video tutorial here.</u></a></p>
      <ol class="lead">
        <li>Go to Stravas website.</li>
        <li>Click the Explore Tab and select Clubs.</li>
        <li>Search and select your club.</li>
        <li>Navigate to the members section of your club.</li>
        <li>In the website link you will see the club Id after www.strava.com/clubs/<strong>THIS_IS_YOUR_CLUB_ID</strong>/members.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
